    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Large baskets, bags, or boxes, often used in pairs, used for transporting objects. These may be carried by a beast of burden; on a person's shoulders or by hand, or mounted on bicycles or automotive vehicles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
